    <title>Flathunt User Guide</title>
    <para>
        <projectname>Flathunt</projectname> is an application that is used to teach you
        programming<!--Toinclude, along with another application named <projectname>Touch</projectname>-->. 
        <projectname>Flathunt</projectname> is a "Scotland
        Yard"-like game that will mainly appear in the assignments for the Introduction to
        Programming course. It is based on the <projectname>Traffic library</projectname> for modeling the city 
        where the game takes place and on <libraryname>EiffelMedia</libraryname> 
        (formerly known as <libraryname>ESDL</libraryname>) for visualization. 
    </para>
